Company Profile:Blackrose Marketing was founded in 2010 by a team of young,
creative and passionate entrepreneurs as a media and marketing based company
under the name Blackrose Media and Marketing. It has recently been incorporated
to Blackrose Marketing Private Limited.We are built on a total commitment to
client requirements and fully dedicated to customized services. We want to
assist you in locating practical solutions with an optimized ROI. Our services
includes all aspects of planning and the provision of concrete solutions
ranging from marketing consultation, event management, event videography,
corporate videos, roadshows, branding and packaging consultation, survey,
market report, and etc.We believe that everyone has a story to tell and with
our integrated marketing approach, we will help to communicate brand messages
to the masses in creating a success story.
Job Description:Responsible for all design activities from conceptualization to completionTo brainstorm and involved in producing new ideas and concepts for publications as well as collateral for the foundationRequire to work with printers for press proofing to ensure quality control for end productsDepending on the competencies developed, new jobs will be introduced.  Job Requirements:Minimum Diploma in Graphics / Multimedia Design.Must be proficient in Photoshop , Illustrator and able to do 3D artworks.Able to work in a fast paced environment and assist in events at times.
